&lt;p&gt;Part Time 25 hours per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We provide care and support to older people in a residential setting at Cottage View.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We do that in a number of ways from providing support to assist with care needs, individual tasks and promoting independence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you think you are committed to enabling and caring for the older person in a residential setting with a flexible approach to work and lead the shift with a willingness and ability to work mornings, evenings, weekends and night cover then this is the job for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; English and/or Welsh speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Christina CreemerRegistered Manager&lt;/p&gt;
